  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Enhancement of Safety and Security of Humanitarians and Field Safety &#x2013; Saving Lives Together</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The purpose of the UNDSS project is to establish a UNDSS presence in Pakistan&#x2019;s KPK (Khyber Pakhtunkhwa) regional districts of Federal Region Bannu, DI Khan, and Lakki Marwat. The establishment of this presence will allow more pro-active and integrated and seamless security and safety support to the UN Pakistan and I/NGO humanitarian response to the evolving IDP crisis in the KPK region.  In particular, UNDSS will establish and operate radio rooms in Bannu and DI Khan districts serving the entire humanitarian community.  The project will run three months.</narrative>
  </description>
